{"type": "article", "id": 63794, "title": "为乳腺癌患者设计的文胸，结合了织物美学和三维模型技术｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-05-15T22:55:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 23350, "name": "DesignByThem"}, {"id": 58593, "name": "Mashoni Design Studio"}, {"id": 58594, "name": "Makers Cabinet"}, {"id": 10763, "name": "CLOT"}, {"id": 58595, "name": "Kuumba International"}, {"id": 58596, "name": "Dion Lee"}, {"id": 58597, "name": "Lisa Marks"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 63, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190515224633RBCD6fbxkuhALtVK.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 14.0px; font: 12.0px Times; color: #0000e9; -webkit-text-stroke: #0000e9; min-height: 14.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>RED / GOLDEN METAL CAN INCENSE BURNER by CLOT x Kuumba</h3><p>创立于 1993 年的生活方式品牌 Kuumba International，香薰一直是其招牌产品。</p><p>最近，曾与 Kuumba 合作多次的时尚品牌 CLOT 再次发出邀请，双方携手推出两款线香燃烧筒，分为金属红和金色，且加入了全新的味道 Cherry Juice。售价 1280 港币，<a href=\"https://www.juicestore.com/collections/clot-1/products/clot-x-kuumba-red-metal-can-incense-burner\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515224821pdHfDUKOm6q7Pl9G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515224820ZWlkiphTurQSoJjU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515224821NU06XEhQGltWVrvC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515224821M27f3j6VLOZoANRG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499642\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515224822FKnzodUVARiIGlr0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905152248225tH4dKpiXAEv9Rjw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Iris by Makers Cabinet</h3><p>伦敦设计工作室 Makers Cabinet 推出了一款名为 Iris 的绘图工具，灵感源自 18 世纪的设计作品，利用照相机镜头光圈的结构。</p><p>Iris 的不锈钢叶片沿实心黄铜外圈内侧旋转，能够绘制出圆形或对圆进行测量，内圈叶片可以随意伸缩成某个特定尺寸。圆的比例用红点标记，因而使用者可以无需其它工具直接读取圆的径。叶片下方还配备天然橡胶底座，可以有效固定工具，防止滑动。刻度尺处还设有标记，使用者可以直接绘制相同或不同尺寸的圆。</p><p>工具的外圈采用实心黄铜加工而成，随时间流逝将产生铜绿。外圈内部包含二十个精心设计的叶片，叶片采用精选弹簧不锈钢压制而成，因而具有耐墨水和耐石墨的特征。这样的材质同时也有助于防止产品变形。</p><p>目前，它在众筹网站 kickstarter 的早鸟价格为 72 英镑，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/brahman/iris-the-drawing-tool-that-inspires-creativity\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515224906UPeR0EQBVmgWtukl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515224906vTEFu0HmWeBy4fs2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515224907FN6YalBo2hCbMe8T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559902\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515224907Zeukn2pz17JfBh43.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515224910gRHjUehOcvP4zfw3.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905152249102kzEQy81dXtleaYW.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Algorithmic Lace bra by Lisa Marks </h3><p>在 2019 年的 LEXUS 雷克萨斯全球设计大奖上，设计师 Lisa Marks 的一款“算法蕾丝文胸”摘得了今年雷克萨斯全球设计大奖的桂冠。</p><p>纺织业早在 19 世纪便率先通过数学算法为纺织品设计各种新的花纹及图案效果。由 Lisa Marks 设计的这款算法蕾丝文胸正是以织物美学设计为灵感，采用源自 16 世纪的复杂蕾丝花边织法，通过古老的编织技艺和先进的三维模型技术，为接受过乳房切除术的乳腺癌幸存者手工设计了这款蕾丝文胸。</p><p>它集美学设计和功能性于一身，在凸显女性优美身形曲线的同时，还可根据胸形进行调整，提升穿戴舒适性。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225144AVFKPNCHY267ciZy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225146ntFHN4rMgixPWODq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225147zwtMQYgkVolEXOPp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225147tZTFr9oJs76HUMAk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.427242\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225211jSZMqCPrG4ctf16e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.550338\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2019/05/13/algorithmic-lace-bra-lisa-marks/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>VITKA Lamp by Mashoni Design Studio</h3><p>斯洛文尼亚设计工作室 Mashoni Design Studio 推出的这个名为 VITKA 的灯具系列，是一种优雅的灯光组合，结合了极简主义艺术。</p><p>几何形式创造了一个引人注目的框架，它容纳了一系列强大的光源，照亮周围地区。</p><p>VITKA 灯具以多支单色金属条制成，用户可因应个人喜好和照明需要，将金属条以不同几何形式组合。灯具上没有按钮，而是借先进的传感电子设备，调控藏于金属条内的灯光暗度，以营造不同的气氛。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225258EUezOnYi6dQqSFPp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225259DoCx71lhaqQEHFir.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225259FGpx2WJ6NOTIvREi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225259jR9P301vFf6GHNBJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225259yWGUKNh0pVO6f4EX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225300pVojBEhZFDGrSW64.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225301IAQHfJUCrW65T8cq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225302Qmy6F0ZMswzhbDIP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225301nqA0N6sfvlu3XQto.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225302x1FAUpw0WVBZKREl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905152253039FebCHUkg1oKan5P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225303ao6SK7fd8lczEhIt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.mashoni.com/en/vitka\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mashoni Design Studio</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The DL Collection by Dion Lee x DesignByThem</h3><p>澳洲时装设计师 Dion Lee 和 DesignByThem 的工业设计师 Sarah Gibson 和 Nicholas Karlovasitis 合作开展了一项新的时尚家具合作项目 DL Collection，在 2019 年米兰设计周上首次亮相。</p><p>通过六轮原型设计和材料实验，这个概念经历了相当长时间的发展。</p><p>DL 休闲椅和 DL 长凳结合了 Dion Lee 和 DesignByThem 的设计特点，他们面临的挑战是将可穿戴材料的转化为功能性物体。Lee 的标志性编织技术的灵感被用于通过金属框架编织耐用的意大利马鞍皮革，以创造流畅的几何形状。</p><p>目前，DL 系列有各种马鞍皮革颜色可供选择，粉末涂层或抛光镀铬框架。售价 1890 美元起，<a href=\"https://www.designbythem.com/collections/dl/products/dl-bench?variant=20074543022168\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225512Y0teDaX5MdJHLxou.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225514oYpqG7rUbP35M9D2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225513OqAH6FyxgtIe8Lpo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905152255185ydSUuB9wpZfkgjb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225519dr206UbFHLNe7saY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.353086\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225519wO3D7FdloArkYXKM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225520VWpH8vCfkXhq61ze.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190515225520gdzutbFIsR17rXKl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.804938\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}